title: Membership
message: All catholic youths between the ages of 15-35 years are mandatory members of the CYON. The members of registered youths are very few, let all who are yet to register endeavour to do so. Let's help move the church forward and spread God's word

title: Drama Rehersals
message: The CYON drama/ cultural group meets every first sunday at 2.00pm. both old and new members are welcome

title: Choir Rehersals
message: The CYON choir unit has it rehearsals every saturday by 5.00pm in the church premises

title: Meeting Time
message: Our meetings are usually held on the first sunday of every month after the 8.00am mass. The dress code for meeting is white and black or the cyon uniforms.
